videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland gets a steal that leads to a Gary Clark layup in the final seconds of the half.
videos.headline: Cincinnati beats the clock on a last second shot

videos.description: South Florida's Malik Fitts makes the and-1 basket on a reverse layup against Cincinnati.
videos.headline: USF's Fitts gets fouled on the acrobatic reverse layup

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland fights for a loose ball and it results in a Jacob Evans one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Evans throws down a thunderous slam for Cincinnati
